  <name>AudioShareGTK</name>
  <summary>Keep the summary shorter, between 10 and 35 characters</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      AudioShareGtk is a Rust-based GTK 4 desktop application that uses Libadwaita for its user interface. It is designed to interact with the audio-share command-line server by mkckr0, enabling audio sharing over a local network.
    </p>
  </description>

